⛳【More Space With Extra Pockets】The golf shoe cleat bags also comes with 2 zipped storage side pockets（might be able to get 6 golf balls in each pocket） and 1 large back pocket, giving you plenty of space to store any additional golf accessories like socks, tees, golf balls, brushes, gloves, spikes, sunglasses, mobile phones, etc. The side pockets of the shoe bag carrier on both ends come in handy when you want to find a few small items.

⛳【Avoid Smelly, Dust-proof, Moisture-proof】This is an excellent quality golf shoe bag men with a double smooth zipped main storage compartment and ventilation on both sides to let the shoes air out. golf shoe organizer helps to prevent that nasty smell or for odor control, and to allow damp shoes to dry. The bottom of this golf shoes bag for men is designed with PU leather film for waterproofing to prevent dust and moisture from entering the shoes.

⛳【Shoe Bag for Any Occasion】The gym bag with shoe compartment is big enough to be multi-functional and can be used to carry sports/casual/formal shoes.YOREPEK travel shoe bag is not just designed for golf shoes but also can be used for other athletic shoes - baseball, basketball, bowling, cycling, camping, and soccer cleats. YOREPEK gym shoe bag also fits dance, yoga, dress shoes, and heels, among others. Or used to carry and travel with your shoes for work etc.

⛳【Unique Design With Claspable Handle】The top of the hanging shoe bag comes with top handle with a detachable buckle that helps you hang your shoes on a golf cart, or to clip them onto your golf bag or wherever you want to hang them.Now golf shoes have a golf trunk organizer no longer have to slide around in the trunk of your car and keep the car trunk clean.It is very suitable for storing dirty golf shoes to prevent grass from getting on the car floor.

Ventilation Mesh Holes The golf shoe bag is equipped with mesh holes on the sides to provide needed ventilation which is for odor control or to allow damp shoes to dry and not produce odor because of storage. Double Solid Zippers The use of smoothly sports drawstring zippers which designs with adding curvature and non-slip design according to finger-use simulation scenarios makes it practical, convenient, and beautiful. Release Buckle On Top The handle with a release buckle on the top which allows you to clip it onto your golf bag easily. reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Perfectly competent golf shoe bag
reviews.reviewText: It is a little padded-feeing and substantial, but I wouldn’t be too rough on the fine/lightweight zippers. It has a couple of vents for air circulation and a couple of side pockets that would fit a couple pairs of ankle socks or something, and another large, flat pocket that’s “paperwork” size, or maybe your pocket s or ears notebook, etc. Look, this isn’t a Coach bag, so it shouldn’t cost a lot. But…it gets the job done.

reviews.reviewText: This is a high-quality, padded shoe bag with two zippered pockets on the sides and one large pocket on the back/bottom (held closed by a small hook-n-loop square in the center of the opening). It even has two air vents to allow the shoes to dry and avoid bad scents.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 7, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Clips on My Golf Bag
reviews.reviewText: This shoe bag is just the right size. My new Adidas golf shoes fit well inside this bag. It also easily clips to my golf bag. There are two ventilation holes in near the top of the bag, with one hole on each side to allow sweaty shoes to air out. The bag is also lightweight enough that I can unclip it, fold it up, and store it in my golf bag while on the course.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 7, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I picked up this shoe bag because I was tired of either putting my golf shoes in my golf bag and getting grass, dirt, and dampness in my bag. It's nice and lightweight. Folds down when nothing is in it. It has plenty of space (I wear 10.5/11) in the main compartment for shoes plus a few extras if needed. There are also two zippered compartments on the sides to hold a few small things if needed. There is also a set of air holes embroidered into the bag so your shoes can dry out inside. If you don't have a shoe bag, this one seems fairly nice for the price.
